snippet.title: VOID DASH TEASER TRAILER
snippet.description:
VOID DASH TEASER TRAILER

Void Dash was created for the AD GAME JAM 2021. It is a simple arcade indie game where you have to dodge asteroids. Void Dash won the second place for graphics in the Game Jam  and is currently still in development with a planned mobile release.

Download VOID DASH: https://deecee03.itch.io/voiddash
Website: https://deeceegames.com/
